        <div id="wicl" class="collapse">
          <p>A car loan helps a person achieve his dream of owning a car. Today having a car, has become a status symbol among people. To help people own a car, banks and NBFC provide car loans.</p>
          <p>A car loan works in a simple pattern. You can take a car loan from a bank and own a car, and repay the loan amount afterward by full payment or monthly installments.</p>
          <p>There are two types of car loans;</p>
          <ul>
            <li>Used car loan-A loan taken to buy a used card is called a used car loan. For example a second-hand car.</li>
            <li>Used car loan-A loan taken to buy a used card is called a used car loan. For example a second-hand car.</li>
          </ul>
