          <a href="javascript:void(0)" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#wituocl">What is a use of the car loan?</a>
        </h4>
        <div id="wituocl" class="collapse">
          <p>A used car loan is also called a pre-owned car loan. A used car loan is taken to buy a car that was previously pre-owned by someone else. A used car loan is most preferred, as a car price depreciates yearly. If you buy a new car now, its price declines to as low as 16% next year. So, instead, it's better to buy a used car. The depreciation rate and insurance on a used car purchase are lower than on a new car.</p>
          <p>The interest rate on the used car starts from 9.25% onwards. The loan tenure for a used car loan is 5-7 years.</p>
